0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"樓下間垃圾翠x貴到仆街，味道連大家樂都不如,都晚晚排長龍喎。係咪位置唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4986789e98b7a1d3773de35b007cd593e9901c4d","tid":481734,"uid":25916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"平靚正 三樣入面有幾多樣"},{"pid":"71dbbf7f6d85c0989368cef373cbbf9adb6aa983","tid":481734,"uid":145769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"最大理由有兩個<br />\n啲野唔好食<br />\n貴過同區30%<br />\n<br />\n好食/平=唔介意污穢，貴，要等<br />\n<br />\n如果同區競爭大<br />\n要睇主要對手實力<br />\n如果咁你轉都無用<br />\n一係轉埋名同班底"},{"pid":"58c66e714896cbc5e7f047fdb091c8817f2af19c","tid":481734,"uid":63307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"玩急口令送汽水"},{"pid":"e545d5169dad7a118a38c56d17c4a1c2dd02a6b3","tid":481734,"uid":82125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"巴打問你幾樣野<br />\n<br />\n1.餐廳位置<br />\n2.好食推介<br />\n3.價錢<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4.最緊要衛生</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n幫唔幫到你就未知，純粹鍾意同朋友放假搵下野食周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b17245c253b09294a6c36c9c83b34baf705919e","tid":481734,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:44:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>家人都係茶記<br />\n早午下午茶尚可<br />\n但晚市就pk<br />\n同條街好多都晚市冇客</blockquote><br />\n而家茶記一個晚餐都要70-80蚊. 食物同LUNCH冇分別.  真係搵鬼食. <br />\n一枝公去食盅頭飯好過. 同女去更加唔洗講."},{"pid":"5bc6f9c4ba4072369299df5ca0215762cec10cdc","tid":481734,"uid":144435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"不如搞兩小時內要食晒好多件雞（明知無可能食得晒）<br />\n<br />\n食唔晒既就客人埋單 <br />\n<br />\n咁撚勁食得晒就抵你free個客"},{"pid":"fce8b2172f15a030bd0469a34adf16e2a6ae4328","tid":481734,"uid":89538,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"真心<br />\n芝士 拉絲 綠茶 紫薯 海膽<br />\n其中揀一兩樣做大佢 唔洗做哂<br />\netc<br />\n芝士xx煲<br />\n綠茶特飲<br />\n大撚把人食 好快仲有人訪問"},{"pid":"47524815c74183de213776c674aeda609a4c39f8","tid":481734,"uid":38898,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊類型既餐廳？ target customer係咩人？</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳，target 係附近屋邨d住客</blockquote><br />\n唔難理解問題所在呀<br />\n<br />\n你問返自己點解唔去某d 餐廳既原因一樣<br />\n<br />\n一係貴，一係唔好食<br />\n<br />\n最重要係客覺得唔值"},{"pid":"16d7912d1f0e62a9068204b5849a5a3c5090dfbc","tid":481734,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"不外乎兩個原因既姐<br />\n<br />\n唔夠對手平 唔夠對手好食<br />\n<br />\n茶記係好食價錢合理既話自然有客"},{"pid":"9672aaa661a0862150807a177839d1ace92363f5","tid":481734,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講多啲間餐廳<br />\n大概食啲咩<br />\n人均消費<br />\n座位<br />\n等等</blockquote><br />\n人均消費：40-50蚊<br />\n座位：30-40</blockquote><br />\n晚飯送甜品/油菜"},{"pid":"137a964bc8bcc354e46fffdab2ff8019df2fb79e","tid":481734,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"開名,  畀連登仔屌幾野,  好快就紅啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615b0d47750abc7faa12036e24ffd6f77b8d1eff","tid":481734,"uid":30831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"最近見到好Q多餐廳整任食火鍋 玩下特色都得既"},{"pid":"7666e2b5c3e75d665cb2a175dbe5a3301d963cd7","tid":481734,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開名,  畀連登仔屌幾野,  好快就紅啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅咗就大力加租，死得仲快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527a799a3e6df7097a47c226aa807820b91a0cff","tid":481734,"uid":58983,"like"