74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"改鋪頭名"},{"pid":"34f29cbae57fa0987fa2b6536e9074e3168d84ac","tid":481734,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"搵新假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f2db45fe03296b1235833894643ff58195181b","tid":481734,"uid":91238,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"1. 搵人係街派Coupon, 用嚟吸引新客 (例如: 憑券午市減3蚊, 晚市減5蚊)<br />\n2. 個客食完飯, 又送多張Coupon比佢, 用嚟Retain舊客<br />\n3. 可以係餐廳門口棟個大大舊嘅牌, 寫住有咩超值午市套餐, 包熱飲, 要比人覺得大件夾抵食, 捉班人貪小便宜心理<br />\n<br />\n仲有小小建議係, 係放學時間係小學門口派宣傳單張, 例如憑券惠顧雞脾餐, 送紅豆冰, 之後細佬扭計就會帶阿媽去, 之後就要箍實班師奶客, 因為佢地多數都係屋企食咩話事果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但Marketing做到點好都好, 都要你嘅嘢好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 現職PR and Marketing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23afcc14fd53019b216a8c8b35dababddf16325d","tid":481734,"uid":49603,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打，做下一人火鍋</blockquote><br />\n其他回覆都係廢 呢個要聽<br />\n一人火鍋 麻辣 online marketing<br />\nThat's it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27094fa9efa21937a4742613e2b03a3d9b0e4ab7","tid":481734,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊類型既餐廳？ target customer係咩人？</blockquote><br />\n茶餐廳，target 係附近屋邨d住客</blockquote><br />\n咩屋邨?私人/公屋/荒山野嶺屋邨?"},{"pid":"b017d31787b3ba7b5ea32c3c8f7e3d10f3c1e1c3","tid":481734,"uid":52294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63f0676d3c216361256cf2c237d52a4dd30f0411","tid":481734,"uid":120053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:11:50.000Z","msg":"擺上新