itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"不如你講下賣咩先得架?<br />\n你隔離又賣咩?<br />\n晚市最緊要個勢，一開頭堆客特登出遲少少比佢<br />\n等多啲人坐係到有人見到就會入黎<br />\n一開頭一定係要儲吓客架了，頂完呢關你就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441a05d23fc2610b2282fa2079e9d7b34453de1d","tid":481734,"uid":156507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"一人任食邊爐/雞煲。 $80/per head<br />\n橫掂都無客, 燈油火蠋/人工/舖租都要俾。 不如旺下人氣先。 <br />\n<br />\n或是。襯冬天做煲仔飯。 $30-40一個。應該好多人食。 都係旺人氣。 旺人流。 和左個開支。<br />\n<br />\n再夜d做埋糖水舖/小食。 可以收夜少少。 eg 1am. 屋邨其實有班夜鬼客架。 <br />\n<br />\n派傳單/郵局通函通知街坊。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你。"},{"pid":"a362bcc74ace5da03548dbab0b473ad7c717b213","tid":481734,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:56:49.000Z","msg":"極邪惡   隱世   芝士  紫薯   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89647d564ca85ec646e17a12f4df5a6e6975d64","tid":481734,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"香港郵政服務寄餐牌coupon"},{"pid":"ccbc6f2ba19f03aadc739f02da6fe8cd7baa9a16","tid":481734,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"晚餐 送碟油菜真係幾吸引"},{"pid":"ef1bd074e90146e10023bbbadf8bc90a57bf9778","tid":481734,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>晚餐 送碟油菜真係幾吸引</blockquote><br />\n唔關事"},{"pid":"d64de30cdb9fa400e92258294b6bbb7c20610e11","tid":481734,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:10:42.000Z","msg":"幾時開始生意轉差左?半年?"},{"pid":"1bade8b3568ad893a302cd7bb6e131a52f5b2e77","tid":481734,"uid":54452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"屌，唔係諗點整好啲野食"},{"pid":"03cd41cb3acc440e44d573e0e62b78d07af4f1b4","tid":481734,"uid":40270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"煲仔飯"},{"pid":"4893d186